      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented release notes; no open critical defects affecting hemolysis-relevant physics.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R1 used under institutional license with version control and change log documentation. No critical defects identified in turbulence or scalar-transport modules relevant to hemolysis prediction."
    },
    {
