      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes published benchmark cases for laminar and turbulent pipe flow within 1% of analytical solution.",
      "rationale": "Fluent 2022 R1 verified against Poiseuille flow and Womersley pulsatile benchmarks. Velocity profiles agree within 0.8% of analytical values, satisfying the required level."
    },
    {
