      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantity of interest (relative hemolysis index RH) is directly linked to clinical hemolysis endpoint and acceptance criterion RH < 1.",
      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH is derived from the same shear-stress exposure integral used in the regulatory submission. The QoI maps directly onto the clinical acceptance criterion and is therefore fully relevant to the COU."
