    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were scoped as not-assessed in accordance with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use. Note: this package conforms to the Minimal profile; the digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and has not been applied to this record.",
